node.text:
#TBT look back at Saturday’s trip for Mahi down in the keys with our CEO John Dorton, @invincibleproteam305_remix, @sarahmelia_fishing, @olympicgoldfishing & @ben_dorton18 

Monitoring the weather, eyes peeled looking for birds working on sprays of bait. This was approaching one of our last spots of the day before heading home 🤙🏽 🚤: 39’ Open Fisherman

#throwbackthursday #whenyoureserious #runandgun #sportfishing #offshorefishing #invincible39 #patented #mpyd #centerconsoleboats #highperformancefishingboats #flkeys #keysfishing #centerconsole #outboards #goboldly #centerconsolesonly

node.text:
We joined the @galeforcetwins both to introduce their dog @firstmatekona to her first mahi, and to share a very important message: Be safe out there this weekend by making sure you always @ridedrydrivedry. 

In partnership with: @uscg @dhsgov 

#boatresponsively #whenyoureserious #ridedrydrivedry #mdw

node.text:
Sending you into the weekend with a 🔥🔥🔥🔥 edit from @_nomadcollective_ for @magnifico_outfitters, a 40' Catamaran based in Texas. They're a fun-loving crew who are just as serious about slaying the fish as they are about their sandbar days. Look out for more from them this summer!
